ins will be forgiven. Whoever stands in prayer during the Night of Decree due to faith and seeking reward, his previous sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/08\/laylat-al-qadar-seven-nights\/","url_meta":{"origin":31658,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last seven nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLook for the Night of Decree in the last ten nights of Ramadan. If one of you is weak or unable, then do not be overcome by the remaining seven nights.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1165 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/last-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":31658,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last ten nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSearch for the Night of Decree in the odd nights among the last ten nights of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1169 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42601,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/02\/abu-rawwad-dua-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":31658,"position":3},"title":"Abu Rawwad on Ramadan: Supplication to start month of fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Walid ibn Muslim reported: Abu Rawwad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cThe Muslims would supplicate at the arrival of Ramadan: O Allah, the month of Ramadan has come. Grant it to me, secure me in it, and accept it from me. O Allah, provide me with its fasting,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/12\/laylat-al-qadr-dua-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":31658,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Laylat al-Qadr: Dua on Night of Decree in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, if I know which night is the Night of Decree, what should I say during it?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, You are pardoning. You love to forgive, so forgive me.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36130,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/laylat-al-qadr-last-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":31658,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Seek Laylat al-Qadr on last night of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Abi Sufyan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek the Night of Decree on the last night of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 2189 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/31658","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href"